  "detailed_description": "Vault Apocalypse is a top-down, roguelite twin-stick arena shooter that brings everything you love about the genre together. Unlock new weapons, accessories and heroes as you discover hundreds of weapon and powerup combinations to keep every run feeling fresh.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.poster.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.webm?t=1718506823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.mp4?t=1718506823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Precision, twin-stick aiming (WASD & Mouse or Gamepad).<br></li><li> Survive waves of diverse monsters and bosses, defeating as many as you can to earn extra gems.<br></li><li> Hundreds of unique powerup, weapon and accessory combinations to explore and master.<br></li><li> Collect experience, level up and tailor your stats to match your playstyle, making each run a unique challenge.<br></li><li> Collect gems and enter the shop to buy new powerups and develop your strategy.<br></li><li> Unlock an evolving arsenal of heroes, weapons, abilities and powerups.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/c298d29d6ba56f981e8ca83c44521e74.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/613efbb6602ac7053f91da4abbe18f23.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=168 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/3f4202c7e8d67f4c7a1ee52c32c14e9f.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/46d08ad457ac51649b89dc834ef44eba.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=74 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Vault Apocalypse is a top-down, roguelite twin-stick arena shooter that brings everything you love about the genre together. Unlock new weapons, accessories and heroes as you discover hundreds of weapon and powerup combinations to keep every run feeling fresh.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.poster.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.webm?t=1718506823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/4edbaf42d2997115889a384ee16f5953.mp4?t=1718506823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Precision, twin-stick aiming (WASD & Mouse or Gamepad).<br></li><li> Survive waves of diverse monsters and bosses, defeating as many as you can to earn extra gems.<br></li><li> Hundreds of unique powerup, weapon and accessory combinations to explore and master.<br></li><li> Collect experience, level up and tailor your stats to match your playstyle, making each run a unique challenge.<br></li><li> Collect gems and enter the shop to buy new powerups and develop your strategy.<br></li><li> Unlock an evolving arsenal of heroes, weapons, abilities and powerups.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/c298d29d6ba56f981e8ca83c44521e74.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569440/extras/613efbb6602ac7053f91da4abbe18f23.avif?t=1718506823\" width=616 height=168 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_i